            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-3acd2624-dd8d-4641-bd69-dd78d7f9e56b">
                Mr. R. Harris
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3acd2624-dd8d-4641-bd69-dd78d7f9e56b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-06-16/debates/03f2bec4-2b16-4b91-a0ec-d841ccbad8ae/CoronationStone#contribution-3acd2624-dd8d-4641-bd69-dd78d7f9e56b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister if, now that the Coronation is done, Her Majesty's Government will consider advising that the Stone of Scone should rest on Scottish territory.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3acd2624-dd8d-4641-bd69-dd78d7f9e56b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-06-16/debates/03f2bec4-2b16-4b91-a0ec-d841ccbad8ae/CoronationStone#contribution-3acd2624-dd8d-4641-bd69-dd78d7f9e56b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-be3be674-b708-4ff5-97d9-7ce17bf6bdae'>
            
<p class="">51.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-af534429-1000-487c-94b2-d46b8c7aa26d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-af534429-1000-487c-94b2-d46b8c7aa26d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-af534429-1000-487c-94b2-d46b8c7aa26d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-af534429-1000-487c-94b2-d46b8c7aa26d">
                Mr. Emrys Hughes
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-af534429-1000-487c-94b2-d46b8c7aa26d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-06-16/debates/03f2bec4-2b16-4b91-a0ec-d841ccbad8ae/CoronationStone#contribution-af534429-1000-487c-94b2-d46b8c7aa26d">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister if, in view of the cost of retaining the Stone of Destiny in Westminster Abbey, he will consider advising that the Stone of Destiny be placed for safe custody in Scotland.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-af534429-1000-487c-94b2-d46b8c7aa26d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-06-16/debates/03f2bec4-2b16-4b91-a0ec-d841ccbad8ae/CoronationStone#contribution-af534429-1000-487c-94b2-d46b8c7aa26d">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-91ba98a7-35f0-4d20-9e9a-1940fee94c0f">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-91ba98a7-35f0-4d20-9e9a-1940fee94c0f">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-91ba98a7-35f0-4d20-9e9a-1940fee94c0f">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-91ba98a7-35f0-4d20-9e9a-1940fee94c0f">
                The Prime Minister (Sir Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-91ba98a7-35f0-4d20-9e9a-1940fee94c0f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-06-16/debates/03f2bec4-2b16-4b91-a0ec-d841ccbad8ae/CoronationStone#contribution-91ba98a7-35f0-4d20-9e9a-1940fee94c0f">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The Coronation Stone has been in Westminster Abbey for over 650 years. It has a special significance for all countries in the Commonwealth, which was strongly reinforced by the Coronation which has just taken place. The decision to restore the Stone to its <span id="734" class="column-number" data-column-number="734"></span> customary position in the Abbey, the traditional place of Coronation, commanded wide acceptance on both sides of the border; and it is not the intention of Her Majesty's present advisers to recommend any change.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-91ba98a7-35f0-4d20-9e9a-1940fee94c0f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-06-16/debates/03f2bec4-2b16-4b91-a0ec-d841ccbad8ae/CoronationStone#contribution-91ba98a7-35f0-4d20-9e9a-1940fee94c0f">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-b26bcf91-9aef-4c71-a403-8b26ac66758c">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-b26bcf91-9aef-4c71-a403-8b26ac66758c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-b26bcf91-9aef-4c71-a403-8b26ac66758c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b26bcf91-9aef-4c71-a403-8b26ac66758c">
                Mr. Hughes
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b26bcf91-9aef-4c71-a403-8b26ac66758c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-06-16/debates/03f2bec4-2b16-4b91-a0ec-d841ccbad8ae/CoronationStone#contribution-b26bcf91-9aef-4c71-a403-8b26ac66758c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is the Prime Minister aware that it costs a great deal to keep this Stone in Westminster Abbey, and that there are special installations which, whenever a Scotsman approaches the Stone, ring a bell in Scotland Yard? On the grounds of economy alone, would it not be far better to take the Stone back to Scotland and put it in a museum, where nobody would want to steal it?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b26bcf91-9aef-4c71-a403-8b26ac66758c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-06-16/debates/03f2bec4-2b16-4b91-a0ec-d841ccbad8ae/CoronationStone#contribution-b26bcf91-9aef-4c71-a403-8b26ac66758c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-3fe1defe-e96a-4e43-ae08-4f2790c8b9f6">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-3fe1defe-e96a-4e43-ae08-4f2790c8b9f6">
