<p class="">Will not my right hon. Friend agree that a final decision on a matter which involves such bitter controversy might well be held over until after the present season of rejoicing, and, particularly, until after Her Gracious Majesty's visit to the capital city of Edinburgh, when we all hope for a maximum of concord and a minimum of discord?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
